			<h2 class="paia__subheading">6. Request Procedure</h2>
			<p class="paia__text">To request access to a record, send a written request to the Information Officer using Form C (available from the Regulator’s website). Include:</p>
			<ul class="paia__list">
				<li>Details of the record</li>
				<li>Preferred form of access</li>
				<li>Proof of identity (if required)</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="paia__subheading">7. Grounds for Refusal</h2>
			<p class="paia__text">Access may be refused if it infringes on:</p>
			<ul class="paia__list">
				<li>Third-party confidentiality or privacy</li>
				<li>Commercial confidentiality</li>
				<li>Unreasonable or excessive resource use</li>
			</ul>

